）<br />\n灣仔、銅鑼灣、天后、炮台山: 維園中央草坪<br />\n鰂魚涌、太古、西灣河、筲箕灣: 沿海旁<br />\n小西灣、杏花邨、柴灣: 柴灣公園<br />\n鑽石山、黃大仙: 黃大仙廣場<br />\n九龍灣、牛頭角、觀塘: 觀塘海濱公園<br />\n大圍、沙田、馬鞍山 : 沙田百步梯<br />\n元朗、天水圍: 天水園公園<br />\n屯門: 屯門公園<br />\n南區: 鴨利洲風之塔公園<br />\n<br />\n仲有獅子山同山頂人鏈!"},{"pid":"8bb7418f5b7c6c5f32dbfc8d1b77e75f26272466","tid":1565363,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T06:20:36.000Z","msg":"可唔可以理解為連登仔已經轉戰國際戰線，用twitter叫緊救命？<br />\n不過少左拉攏中間派既文宣係唔理想既"},{"pid":"bddde075974c0d6acc7f53f4241d36214f0bc21a","tid":1565363,"uid":279840,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8bb7418f5b7c6c5f32dbfc8d1b77e75f26272466","tid":1565363,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T06:20:36.000Z","msg":"可唔可以理解為連登仔已經轉戰國際戰線，用twitter叫緊救命？<br />\n不過少左拉攏中間派既文宣係唔理想既"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T06:31:04.000Z","msg":"其實2014運動其中一個死因就係過份圍爐， 冇集中火力打廢老戰線， 爭取中間派甚至淺藍。<br />\n我哋開局個陣文宣隊有至少4成火力係中間人士。<br />\n而家呢？<br />\n日日爆眼， 警暴， 集中晒自己友到。 <br />\n<br />\n我哋而家要打就係區選戰， 要民主力量大勝區選政府， <br />\n發動以農村（區議會）包圍城市（立法會）戰略"},{"pid":"83ec0c6daab5301c1a43ea8b341e4c487c023691","tid":1565363,"uid":281342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T06:45:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gZH76Gs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgZH76Gs.jpg&h=45845535&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NrSLTms.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNrSLTms.jpg&h=ad8f0a00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T92zMGs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT92zMGs.jpg&h=fc02c1d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QGQhKs8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQGQhKs8.png&h=e64c2b4f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sUyfv78.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsUyfv78.jpg&h=31b8513